# How to assemble a frame?
To assemble the frame one need to take top and bottom and connect them together.  <br />
The pinion gear needs also some modifications, the horn which is usually available together with the servo, needs to be modified. <br />
To make a working pinion gear one need to take one of the horns, which are usually available together with the servo, and cut the arm, such that only the round part remains. It is probably the best to take the horn with only one arm, shown on the photo below.
